column2:
"Well then, next is my order
The other day, I took a lot of screenshots in my room with Tetra..."
"I want to take some more in a location that feels a bit more, you know... open<white><pict cute_icon><c>"
"I want to go on a quest with Tetra to somewhere that has beautiful scenery, but I won't be able to focus if there's enemies around..."
"If it's not too much to ask, could you come with us as an escort?"

"I'll give you my Partner Card, so give me and Tetra a call whenever you're ready
Take good care of us"
